import "./at.css" export default function At3() { return (

You’re a human magnet

  • We become what we think about
  • What the mind can conceive and believe the mind can achieve
  • A man is what he thinks about all day long
  • There is nothing on earth you cannot have once you have mentally accepted the fact you can have it
  • Whether you think you can or cannot you are always right
  • You can’t expect positive result when you spend 10 seconds of the day thinking positively and remaining 16 hours of the day dwelling on negative outcomes
  • There is only one positive outcome but several negative outcomes
) }
